data.description: Introducing this charming Cape Coral home! Nestled in the peaceful Pelican neighborhood , this property offers a perfect blend of comfort and style. With 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, there's ample space for the whole family. The open-concept living area and kitchen make entertaining a breeze. Step outside to the spacious backyard that offers privacy as well as room for a pool or pets. There is a concrete patio that could have a screened in area added.  Conveniently located near, many schools K-12, restaurants, shopping centers, and within 0.4 miles to Pelican baseball and soccer sports complex. This home promises a relaxed Florida lifestyle. Don't miss this opportunity to make it yours! Schedule a showing today.
